09-07T15:28:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"69e87654a5f800b83f32f80ffecf31bc169938f1","tid":1550300,"uid":298610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:34:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> FIGHT FOR FREEDOM!!"},{"pid":"2558b176ec2bec651a8e1eb11b62ced3157b95c7","tid":1550300,"uid":6891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:34:47.000Z","msg":"資助學生入場睇波呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"194dec7c52985751830a76d7c94981b38b2d6a36","tid":1550300,"uid":45035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:22:15.000Z","msg":"第一次睇波 應該要買邊個座位"},{"pid":"512364a898ab63fa15d0c102bd4469178e73de57","tid":1550300,"uid":298610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"194dec7c52985751830a76d7c94981b38b2d6a36","tid":1550300,"uid":45035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:22:15.000Z","msg":"第一次睇波 應該要買邊個座位"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T2